(35, 'Havana Nha Trang Hotel', '38 Tr·∫ßn Ph√∫, L·ªôc Th·ªç, Kh√°nh H√≤a, 650000, Vietnam', 5, '02583889999', NULL, 'https://havanahotel.vn/', '<p>Havana Nha Trang Hotel offers modern accommodations just 5 minutes\' walk from 2/4 Square. The sandy beach is just across the street. An outdoor pool, spa treatments and a fitness center are available. Fitted with free WiFi, all guestrooms are nonsmoking and come with a flat-screen TV. A personal safe and electric kettle are included. The private bathroom has a bathtub and free toiletries. Havana Nha Trang Hotel is 25 mi from Nha Trang Airport. Parking is free, while airport transfers are available at a charge. Both Asian and international dishes are served at Spicy Restaurant. A buffet breakfast is available, or guests can also opt for in-room dining. Day trips and car rentals can be arranged at the tour desk. The hotel also provides a business center, babysitting services and a 24-hour front desk.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/RwIi0nVQTng6ltAVTPh7.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/0FKLbZIlCoP57U8rV8U6.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:53:08', '2024-01-16 08:53:08', 1, 'havana-nha-trang-hotel', NULL, 'Havana Nha Trang Hotel offers modern accommodations just 5 minutes\' walk from 2/4 Square. The sandy beach is just across the street. An outdoor pool, spa treatments and a fitness center are available.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.0707946496823!2d109.19326247495576!3d12.24348578800894!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31706778fd8c5dff%3A0xd3c343b165958165!2sPremier%20Havana!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705395162194!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"me