(36, 'Liberty Central Nha Trang Hotel', '9 Bi·ªát Th·ª±, L·ªôc Th·ªç, Nha Trang, Kh√°nh H√≤a 650000, Vietnam', 4, '02583529555', NULL, 'http://www.libertycentralnhatrang.com/', '<p>Conveniently located, Liberty Central Nha Trang Hotel offers luxurious and elegant accommodations with free WiFi access throughout the property. It features an outdoor pool, sauna, fitness center and meeting/banquet facilities on site. The hotel is just 656 feet from Nha Trang Beach and 984 feet from Vietnam Sailing Center. Nha Trang Airport is approximately 17 mi away. Tastefully furnished, air-conditioned rooms and suites come equipped with a wardrobe, personal safe, a flat-screen cable TV and seating area. Mini-bar and electric kettle are also included. Offering shower facility, the private bathroom has slippers and bathrobes. At Liberty Central Nha Trang Hotel, guests can indulge in a pampering massage at the spa, or enjoy a karaoke session on site. Operating a 24-hour front desk, the friendly staff can assist with laundry, airport transfers and concierge services. The in-house restaurant serves an appetizing selection of local and Continental dishes. After-meal drinks can be enjoyed at the bar.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/aMRFWDWsfrXz4yaNBuH5.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/tkIqOedf86anRjkUDGPr.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:54:36', '2024-01-16 08:54:36', 1, 'liberty-central-nha-trang-hotel', NULL, 'Conveniently located, Liberty Central Nha Trang Hotel offers luxurious and elegant accommodations with free WiFi access throughout the property. It features an outdoor pool, sauna, fitness center and meeting/banquet facilities on site.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.1867673804118!2d109.19309357495557!3d12.235629988016228!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3170677b4bda091b%3A0xdd08e93dd8cf8989!2sLiberty%20Central%20Nha%20Trang!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705395254254!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=