(37, 'Silkotel Hoi An', '14 Hung Vuong Street, Cam Pho, Hoi An, Vietnam', 4, '02353963399', NULL, 'https://hoian.silkotel.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<p data-et-view=\"eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">You\'re eligible for a Genius discount at Silkotel Hoi An! To save at this property, all you have to do is&nbsp;<a class=\"bui-link\" href=\"https://account.booking.com/auth/oauth2?aid=357028&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.booking.com%2Flogin.html%3Fop%3Doauth_return&amp;client_id=vO1Kblk7xX9tUn2cpZLS&amp;state=UoUCXk7utcQPMgBkI6CB7XjvAXO7fGm7_ROlRWoThAipplGdeL9QWIm2Jm3a64GEA_4Ked5d_nMoGNDw69Q6TNBvVdZeF4_cdNpn2KzOiw5FPV6NS1Uy_Q_2GYsp48qiVVWMm3lgls8N1y_lljzrqDzHaUaabJmZws8piL-RSY_Ixf0W7keAjVi9nTXHgPiDF4USe2PPYpVJC5C5m5VrVn1SzU9XwS7ORUP8dQQFgFQWjpRY9NChdMTnzgR_3Tlq3pb5A9qkEXVfx7dKRCoInPfQG-bvIdmbuyzMDoDAdkQ3wdN4-3zrqo088SHTej3ohu7q_wZVC6noZpM30vzh9HvkzxrGXU22&amp;bkng_action=hotel&amp;lang=en-gb&amp;response_type=sso&amp;dt=1705395215\" data-et-click=\"customGoal:eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">sign in</a>.</p>\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Located in the heart of tranquil Hoi An, Silkotel Hoi An offers relaxing accommodation in Hoi An. It features a spa and fitness centre, swimming pool and an on-site restaurant that offers both local and international delights. Massage services are available at additional charges. Free WiFi is available throughout the property. The air-conditioned rooms at Silkotel Hoi An all come with a TV, separate seating area, safety deposit box and electric kettle. The en suite bathroom is fitted with either bath or shower facilities, hairdryer, slippers, bathrobes and free toiletries. At the property you will also find a sun terrace, barbecue facilities, a tour desk, luggage storage and