(64, 'InterContinental ƒê√† N·∫µng Sun Peninsula Resort', 'Bai Sac, Son Tra Peninsula, Danang, Vietnam', 5, '02363938888', NULL, 'Bai Sac, Son Tra Peninsula, Danang, Vietnam', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Experience World-class Service at InterContinental Danang Sun Peninsula Resort, an IHG Hotel</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Boasting several fine dining options like the acclaimed La Maison 1888, InterContinental Danang Sun Peninsula Resort provides a luxurious retreat with private beach, a 2 large outdoor swimming pools and a spa. Spectacular views of the ocean can be enjoyed from the resort. All accommodations are luxuriously decorated and provide private balconies. The resort&rsquo;s beachfront villas are nestled within spectacular boulders at the foot of the mountain and come with private pools, a sundeck and luxurious bathroom facilities. Select rooms have a spa bath and a private dining pavilion offering magnificent ocean views. It takes 45 minutes from the hotel to Danang Airport and 30 minutes to Ngu Hanh Son. Cham Museum is about 16 mi away, while The Imperial City of Hu·∫ø, The Old Town of H·ªôi An and the M·ªπ S∆°n ruins, popular UNESCO World Heritage sites are about 28 mi from the hotel. Visit the world-acclaimed Bana Hills Golf Club or challenge yourself at the Danang Golf Club. The resort&rsquo;s many recreational options include cycling, yoga and hiking. Alternatively, guests can request for pampering massage and body treatments at the spa. There is also a modern fitness center on site. Enjoy fresh Vietnamese delicacies in private booths, 328 feet above sea level at Citron Restaurant. For a relaxed beachfront dining experience, visit Barefoot and sample delicious grilled meats and fresh seafood paired with cocktails and wines. Buffalo Bar serves vintage champagne and premium hand-rolled cigars.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.4</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/vWGDHRbFpTVbTzjpwhdb.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/u3BYFmem3YfM0UVPJCWZ.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:29:33', '2024-01-16 09:29:33', 1, 'intercontinental-da-nang-sun-peninsula-resort', NULL, 'Boasting several fine dining options like the acclaimed La Maison 1888, InterContinental Danang Sun Peninsula Resort provides a luxurious retreat with private beach, a 2 large outdoor swimming pools and a spa. Spectacular views of the ocean can be enjoyed from the resort.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3832.900168159531!2d108.3027337741528!3d16.122464384564765!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31423d9513ec9199%3A0x5ade8a2bd4daad0d!2sInterContinental%20%C4%90%C3%A0%20N%E1%BA%B5ng%20Sun%20Peninsula%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705397318502!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
