(70, 'Unique Mui Ne Resort and Spa', '20 b Nguy·ªÖn ƒê√¨nh Chi·ªÉu, Ph∆∞·ªùng H√†m Ti·∫øn, Th√†nh ph·ªë Phan Thi·∫øt, B√¨nh Thu·∫≠n, Vietnam', 0, '0938235535', NULL, 'http://www.uniquevn.com/', '<p>Unique Mui Ne Resort and Spa features an outdoor pool on its private beach and a rooftop restaurant overlooking Muine Bay. It provides spacious air-conditioned rooms with private balconies, free Wi-Fi and buffet breakfast. Featuring sea views and cool breezes, the modern rooms boast over-sized windows and classic wood furnishings. They have a flat-screen satellite TV, tea/coffee maker and a private bathroom. A relaxing massage and beauty treatments can be enjoyed at the spa and hair salon. Other leisure options include a hot tub, steam baths and water sports. The rooftop restaurant offers hearty international menus while the Poolside Restaurant Bar &amp; Lounge serves pizzas and cocktails. Room service is available. Resort Unique Mui Ne is a 20-minute drive from Phan Thiet&acirc; city center and 124 mi from Ho Chi Minh City. It provides charged airport transfers and free parking.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/CITqjjeIfYsfcbbSs0br.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/zJjhSJ1pet34spVtaZ5f.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:35:31', '2024-01-16 09:35:31', 1, 'unique-mui-ne-resort-and-spa', NULL, 'Unique Mui Ne Resort and Spa features an outdoor pool on its private beach and a rooftop restaurant overlooking Muine Bay. It provides spacious air-conditioned rooms with private balconies, free Wi-Fi and buffet breakfast.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3917.2761534353335!2d108.19256207493524!3d10.9425000892165!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31768e4b454337c3%3A0xf2b819ee3b839fa9!2sUnique%20Mui%20Ne%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705397713450!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaur