(101, 'KOBI Onsen Resort Hue', 'GJC7+C97, M·ªπ An, Ph√∫ Vang, Th·ª´a Thi√™n Hu·∫ø 53000, Vietnam', 5, NULL, NULL, 'https://kobionsenresorthue.com/', '<p>KOBI Onsen Resort Hue (Formerly Kawara My An Onsen Resort) &ndash; a wellness resort complex of traditional Japanese onsen standards, one of the characteristic projects of BBGroup in Central Vietnam With the mission of a pioneer in the creation of symbols, BB Group comes to Hue with its earnest desires to develop and create novel tourism impressions to this ancient capital. Thanks to the technology transfer and operation experience from Kawara Resort - one of the famous traditional hot spring resort brands in Japan, we hope to provide visitors with an experience of a high-class resort complex, especially the onsen service of notable Japanese standards, and most of all, a cross-cultural exchange between the Land of the Rising Sun and Hue Citadel. Located around 1.2 mi from No Market and 5 mi from Dong Ba Market, the resort is also 4.3 mi away from Trang Tien Bridge. Guests can enjoy a drink at the bar or a meal in the restaurant. A buffet breakfast can be enjoyed at the property. Guests can make use of the fitness center. Staff at reception can help around the clock with advice on the area. Tinh Tam Lake is 6.8 mi from KOBI Onsen Resort Hue, while Museum of Royal Antiquities is 6.8 mi away. The nearest airport is Phu Bai Airport, 16 mi from the resort.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/GtaSvqL3rWW6rC2ySL4f.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/f2gOoXvKdXZrkSoGqKdL.png\"]', '2024-01-16 10:13:08', '2024-01-16 10:13:08', 1, 'kobi-onsen-resort-hue', NULL, 'KOBI Onsen Resort Hue (Formerly Kawara My An Onsen Resort) ‚Äì a wellness resort complex of traditional Japanese onsen standards, one of the characteristic projects of BBGroup in Central Vietnam', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3825.1001412685023!2d107.61085487482258!3d16.521041284225863!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3141a