(118, 'Ana Mandara Villas Dalat Resort & Spa', '2 ƒê∆∞·ªùng L√™ Lai, Ph∆∞·ªùng 5, Th√†nh ph·ªë ƒê√† L·∫°t, L√¢m ƒê·ªìng, Vietnam', 5, '02633555888', NULL, 'http://anamandara-resort.com/', '<p>For those who are inspired by history and style, look no further than Ana Mandara Villas Dalat Resort &amp; Spa. It is one-of-a-kind hideaway yet centrally located treasure; tranquil and captivating sanctuary consisting of of 17 elegant villas with French architecture that date back to a century ago. Delicately blended in a lush landscape on top of a hill, Ana Mandara Villas Dalat Resort &amp; Spa offers exceptional experiences in service, serenity and enjoyment. For its classical charming architecture, charismatic interior and unerring attention to detail that offers unique experiences in simplicity, serenity and refinement, Ana Mandara Villas Dalat Resort &amp; Spa has been repeatedly awarded as World Luxury Hotel Awards in 2018, Leading Luxury Mountain Resort in 2019, Travelers\' Choice Awards in 2021 by TripAdvisor and other platforms. The resort&rsquo;s La Cochinchine Spa provides 5 treatment rooms with a wide range of therapeutic treatments including foot massage area and different sauna and steam baths. The resort operates a tour desk and 24-hour front desk, providing a range of services, including currency exchange, car rental and airport transfer. If you&rsquo;re looking for a luxurious and romantic dining experience, Le Petit Restaurant serves both Vietnamese &amp; Western cuisine showcasing the freshest ingredients from Dalat and our own organic kitchen garden. Once a French colonial villa, Le Petit has maintained its classical design, becoming a destination dining experience. A brand new addition to Le Petit Private Dining Room is La Table Des Lys service, providing exceptional fine-dining experience for gourmets. Guests can go exploring the surrounding landscaped areas and local culture and farming countryside. Within 1.9 mi, you can reach many popular points of interest of Da Lat, such as Lam Vien Square, Xuan Huong Lake and Dalat Flower Gardens. The nearest airport is Lien Khuong Airport, 14 mile away.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/z2xcepK7WKjMIRpvIlRq.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/E9Zt9Pf68RD7m4Jhm0jR.png\"]', '2024-01-17 01:26:29', '2024-01-17 01:26:29', 1, 'ana-mandara-villas-dalat-resort-and-spa', NULL, 'For those who are inspired by history and style, look no further than Ana Mandara Villas Dalat Resort & Spa. It is one-of-a-kind hideaway yet centrally located treasure; tranquil and captivating sanctuary consisting of of 17 elegant villas with French architecture that date back to a century ago. Delicately blended in a lush landscape on top of a hill, Ana Mandara Villas Dalat Resort & Spa offers exceptional experiences in service, serenity and enjoyment.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3903.4395608883387!2d108.42102507472973!3d11.944038988284756!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31716cd40cc0684b%3A0x6b9892057c05b737!2sAna%20Mandara%20Villas%20Dalat%20Resort%20%26%20Spa!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705454771142!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 15),
