(120, 'BlueSun Hotel Danang', '230 Vo Nguyen Giap Street, Phuoc My ward, Son Tra, Danang, Vietnam', 4, '02363960000', NULL, 'https://bluesunhotel.com.vn/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Located in the picturesque coastal city of Da Nang, BlueSun Hotel Danang offers stylish accommodations by the beach. Bluesun features an indoor pool, fitness center and a hot tub for you to indulge in. Guests can enjoy their choice of cocktail or drinks at the on-site bar, or simply relax on the terrace, while enjoying views of the sea. Free WiFi is available throughout the property. Each air-conditioned room at the hotel offers a sophisticated atmosphere with beige interiors and modern furnishing. All rooms come equipped with a TV for entertainment, while a kettle is available for your convenience. Private bathrooms are fitted with a shower or bathtub, while bathrobes, slippers and toiletries are provided. Rooms are accessible via elevators. The 24-hour front desk staff are available to assist with services such as currency exchange, tour and ticketing, luggage storage, as well as other concierge services. Guests can also enjoy a massage at the property, or shop for a gift or groceries at the shops on-site. Shuttle services are available at a fee. The elegant on-site restaurant located on the 15th floor serves an array of traditional Vietnamese dishes, as well as international cuisines during breakfast, lunch and dinner. Song Han Bridge is 1.2 mi from BlueSun Hotel Danang, while Cham Museum is 1.6 mi from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 3.7 mi from the property.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.3</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/mvVriBM9PgcYgs5VhbrJ.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/tIbrRE7OgwCKHNnLBvwb.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 06:56:34', '2024-01-17 06:56:34', 1, 'bluesun-hotel-danang', NULL, 'Located in the picturesque coastal city of Da Nang, BlueSun Hotel Danang offers stylish accommodations by the beach. Bluesun features an indoor pool, fitness center and a hot tub for you to indulge in. Guests can enjoy their choice of cocktail or drinks at the on-site bar, or simply relax on the terrace, while enjoying views of the sea. Free WiFi is available throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d4559.390038174087!2d108.24213749738696!3d16.066800606405163!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31421783ecd4eb7f%3A0x28000e5dd697ce2b!2sBlueSun%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705474556577!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(121, 'Cicilia Hotels & Spa Danang', 'No.06-08-10 Do Ba street, T20 Beach, Ngu Hanh Son District, Da Nang, Vietnam', 4, '02363747888', NULL, 'http://ciciliadanang.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Cicilia Hotels &amp; Spa Danang is a captivating blend of luxury decor and Vietnamese influences, offering a delightful stay in the vibrant city of Da Nang. Located just less than a minute\'s walk away from the stunning My Khe Beach, the strategic location of Cicilia Danang Hotels &amp; Spa makes it an ideal choice for both leisure and business travelers. The hotel boasts two outdoor swimming pools that provide breathtaking panoramic views of the sea, creating a serene atmosphere for unwinding and soaking up the beauty of the surroundings. The property is ideally located within 15 minutes drive from Da Nang International airport, 4 kilometers to the city center and 4 kilometers to Han Market. For those interested in exploring the natural wonders of the area, the renowned Marble Mountains, a cluster of limestone and marble hills, are within easy reach at around 5 kilometers away. The hotel provides a variety of well-appointed rooms and suites suitable for single travelers, couples, triples and families. Each room is thoughtfully designed to ensure your utmost comfort and convenience throughout your stay. Featuring amenities such as a flat-screen TV, a cozy seating area, and a kettle in every room, we aim to provide you with all the essential elements for a pleasant and enjoyable experience. Guests can approach the 24-hour front desk for currency exchange, tour arrangements and concierge services. A fitness center is available for working out. Alternatively, guests can indulge in a variety of spa treatments from Cicilia Spa. The in-house restaurants serve up an array of Asian and continental delights. Children Policy: According to hotel policy and restrictedly set up in Booking.com website, 2 children under 12 years old are allowed to stay with their parents, in detail: - The 1st child 0-4 years old stays for free if using the existing bed. - Children 5-11 years old will be charged VND 200.000 per child per night if using the existing bed. - Children from 12 years old and above require an extra bed with additional cost at 400,000 VND per child per night (only some rooms can place extra beds, kindly check the room description and capacity). Please double check your reservation. In case you have not provided us with the number and age of children when you make this reservation, please pay the children surcharge at the hotel. The roof top swimming pool is under renovation until the end of November 2023. Guest still can enjoy the pool on the 3rd floor.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>8.9</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/8QW93lPvy61kcB4A1OO2.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/Qt0Mp0nap9hQFBa8P7Gd.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 06:58:54', '2024-01-17 06:58:54', 1, 'cicilia-hotels-and-spa-danang', NULL, 'Cicilia Hotels & Spa Danang is a captivating blend of luxury decor and Vietnamese influences, offering a delightful stay in the vibrant city of Da Nang. Located just less than a minute\'s walk away from the stunning My Khe Beach, the strategic location of Cicilia Danang Hotels & Spa makes it an ideal choice for both leisure and business travelers.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d5422.459968607209!2d108.24377506332885!3d16.052084972345746!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3142177ae0bde10f%3A0x1b8b3008a40e9c3f!2sCicilia%20Hotels%20%26%20Spa%20Danang!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705474704923!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(122, 'Maximilan Danang Beach Hotel', '222 Vo Nguyen Giap, Son Tra District, Da Nang, Vietnam', 4, '02363798799', NULL, 'http://maximilan.com.vn/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Situated in Da Nang, 500 metres from My Khe Beach, Maximilan Danang Beach Hotel features accommodation with free bikes, free private parking, an outdoor swimming pool and a fitness centre. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a shared lounge and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The accommodation offers a 24-hour front desk, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests. At the hotel the rooms have air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a bidet, free toiletries and a hairdryer. Each room has a kettle, while some rooms are fitted with a kitchen with a fridge, an oven and a microwave. At Maximilan Danang Beach Hotel every room comes with bed linen and towels. The accommodation offers a terrace. Bac My An Beach is 2.8 km from Maximilan Danang Beach Hotel, while Love Lock Bridge Da Nang is 2.2 km from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 5 km from the hotel.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.5</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/hFp1V3iaAw6cNBoIZ9Jo.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/8PzVDxceTLzX4IutFgVA.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:01:35', '2024-01-17 07:01:35', 1, 'maximilan-danang-beach-hotel', NULL, 'Situated in Da Nang, 500 metres from My Khe Beach, Maximilan Danang Beach Hotel features accommodation with free bikes, free private parking, an outdoor swimming pool and a fitness centre. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a shared lounge and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The accommodation offers a 24-hour front desk, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3833.9666082337462!2d108.24236677415132!3d16.067222484611978!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314217d4981af15b%3A0xb26adaa1034f9b59!2sMaximilan%20Danang%20Beach%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705474849013!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(123, 'HAIAN Beach Hotel & Spa', '278 Vo Nguyen Giap, Da Nang, Vietnam', 4, '02362228666', NULL, 'http://haianbeachhotelspa.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">This property is 1 minute walk from the beach. The Hotel offers elegantly well-appointed rooms and suites with great views toward the ocean and the city. The Hotel also boasts an infinity rooftop pool where guests can swim or leisurely enjoy the sunlight on the sunbeds. All rooms are well-furnished with modern d&eacute;cor and facilities including air conditioner, a flat-screen TV, minibar, wardrobe and comfortable seating area. The en suite private bathroom is equipped with a bath or shower, hair dryer and free toiletries. For your comfort, you will find bathrobes and slippers. Guests can have a meal at the in-house restaurant featuring delicacies ranging from international delights to traditional Vietnamese cuisine. Coffee Lounge and Bar is also available for guests to grab a drink. Staff at the 24-hour front desk can assist with a variety of services, including private check-in or check-out, luggage storage, concierge and tour desk. Guests can also use the facilities in the business centre. Guests enjoy free afternoon tea daily at the property. HAIAN Beach Hotel &amp; Spa also provides free airport transfer service. HAIAN Beach Hotel &amp; Spa is just 15-minute drive from Danang International Airport and 30-minute drive from Hoi An Ancient Town. The Hotel is 2.2 km from Dragon Bridge, 3.1 km from Song Han Bridge.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.6</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/LpAIir5nK22G0ccRXNkk.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/t0unj6NP533gGBegizBV.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:03:53', '2024-01-17 07:03:53', 1, 'haian-beach-hotel-and-spa', NULL, 'This property is 1 minute walk from the beach. The Hotel offers elegantly well-appointed rooms and suites with great views toward the ocean and the city. The Hotel also boasts an infinity rooftop pool where guests can swim or leisurely enjoy the sunlight on the sunbeds.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3834.2397443660766!2d108.24495327415097!3d16.053044184624117!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3142177a5e88b85b%3A0x6efe50bad84535c3!2sHaian%20Beach%20Hotel%20%26%20Spa!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705475018868!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16);
